{"tid":704118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Vox: 中國成為最大贏家","createTime":"2018-06-16T07:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T09:36:49.000Z","uid":96715,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"587559b9daa7c567f1bc0723ae4df05a618ac8ed","tid":704118,"uid":96715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"美國著名新聞網站Vox，被發現收取中國政府支持的組織資金，撰寫軟性新聞文章。<br />\n<br />\n最近Vox外電編輯Yochi Dreazen一篇新聞，標題為「特金會最大贏家？中國」（The big winner of the Trump-Kim summit? China）。在文章底部，特別註明了它是由中美交流基金會資助。<br />\n<br />\n文章最底的註解寫道：「這篇報道是由中美交流基金會（CUSEF）資助，它是一間總部在香港的私人資助非牟利機構，致力『促使中美兩國的政策制定者、商界領袖、學者、智庫、文化界及教育工作者，進行開放且有建設性的交流』。」這個介紹跟中美交流基金會網站的英文介紹用字同出一轍。<br />\n<br />\n中美交流基金會是中國政府支持的組織，在海外宣傳中國，「廣告新聞」首先由《華爾街日報》專欄作家Josh Rogin發現。Rogin在Twitter質問Vox：「你知道CUSEF由中國共產黨內具影響力的一名高級官員當主席，對吧？（他就是）董建華，CUSEF的主席是中國全國政協副主席，（全國政協）與在海外推動黨目標的統戰部有關係。」<br />\n<br />\n目前，美國國會議員致力反擊中國利用美國傳媒作政治宣傳，Vox跟中美交流基金會的關係更受關注。參議院2018年度國防授權法案中，特別提到「中國正透過影響美國傳媒、文化機構、商家、學術及政策社群，對其安全、軍事政策和目標更加有利」。近月，中美交流基金會也因為被指滲透德州大學奧斯汀分校，被美國國會盯上。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180615/58320123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320123&d=pf22FSXlZHl%2F3nQR5BVjv6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=581b6c3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320123&h=7ee1f913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180615/58320123</a><br />\n<br />\nVox source: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.vox.com/platform/amp/world/2018/6/13/17458944/trump-kim-summit-china-response-south-korea-military-drills\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fplatform%2Famp%2Fworld%2F2018%2F6%2F13%2F17458944%2Ftrump-kim-summit-china-response-south-korea-military-drills&d=pf22FSXlZHl%2F3nQR5BVjv6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=8ec898e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.vox.com/platform/amp/world/2018/6/13/17458944/trump-kim-summit-china-response-south-korea-military-drills</a><br />\n<br />\n真係人唔笑 狗都吠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b46fae482ab0a1ba6d2329e9b77469f13466e4","tid":704118,"uid":96715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59fb3ea7c40cf31989caa1ce12418ea1b44dbd0","tid":704118,"uid":96715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:00:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82b7589ef1049a99596df2fdefca6a9f291acfe","tid":704118,"uid":96715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76510716c6e8f4df0c757f4fe2c6eae1c8f87fa5","tid":704118,"uid":96715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab478450732e46d09ac65f504acb0b57d495bf80","tid":704118,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"The big winner<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93861a4a4b1c55aaa602f1566f16573637491c59","tid":704118,"uid":96715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}